    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "Finally I found the root cause of the problem.  In the pom.xml file (FdxClient project) 1.6 value makes it. &lt;plugin&gt; \t&lt;artifactId&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt; \t&lt;configuration&gt; \t\t&lt;source&gt;1.6&lt;/source&gt; \t\t&lt;target&gt;1.6&lt;/target&gt; \t\t&lt;encoding&gt;cp1254&lt;/encoding&gt; \t&lt;/configuration&gt; &lt;/plugin&gt;"
  } ],
