    "body" : "<p>I had the same case mentionned by @lordbao, but I couldn't delete using project structure (the popup of error blocked acces to my project).</p>\n<p>My solution was to change directly in .iml file for my project :</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A module file (the .iml file) is used for keeping module configuration</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It's an xml file you can delete the duplicated entry for sourceFolder tag.</p>\n"
